WhoWeAreText: Welcome to ComETS, We are a student club from the École de Technologie Supérieure dedicated to designing and building electric motorcycles. Our team of passionate students works to push the boundaries of sustainable engineering while participating in international competitions.
InnovationText: We design, assemble, and race high-performance electric motorcycles. From concept to competition, our members innovate and learn by tackling technical challenges in events such as MotoStudent, NJMP, and AHRMA.
